bootdialogue : all
{
	"\1\s[15]\0\s[0]%(normtext)\b[0]Another long day... \_w[1200]\n\n[half]Work has been hectic today, \_w[800]I was hardly able to keep up with it all. \_w[800]Didn't help that I haven't been able to move around for too long without losing my breath.\_w[1200]\n\n[half]My chest gets too tight whenever that happens, \_w[800]almost feels like something lodged in my lungs...\_w[1200]\nI've tried coughing \f[bold,1]something\f[bold,0] out but I haven't had any luck.\_w[1200]\nAt least now I have some time to myself. \_w[1200]Now I can finally rest...\_w[2400]\n\n[half]"
	"\_w[3600]I really need to fix this place up sometime... \_w[1200]it's okay but something about it seems... off.\_w[1200]\n\n[half]"
	"\_w[4800]Has that spot on the wall gotten bigger?\f[italic,0]\_w[2400]\n\n[half]"
	"\1\s[11]%(fliptext)˙\w9\w9˙\w9\w9˙\w9\w9\f[bold,0]\_w[2400]\n\n[half]"
	"\0\s[0]%(normtext)What is that?! \_w[800]Did that thing just move??\f[italic,0]\_w[2400]\n\n[half]"
	"\1\s[10]%(fliptext)˙\w9\w9˙\w9\w9˙\w9\w9\f[bold,0]\_w[2400]\n\n[half]"
	"\0\s[0]%(normtext)!\_w[1200]\n\n[half]"
	"\1\s[10]%(fliptext)˙˙˙ollǝɥ ˙˙˙ɥ\f[bold,0]"
}

