bootdialoguedayone
{
	"\1\s[12]\0\s[0]%(normtext)\_w[2100].\w9\w9.\w9\w9.\w9\w9I'm still here... \_w[1800]I...\w9\w9 don't feel any worse at least...\_w[1200]\nWhat time is it...?\n\_w[2400]! \w9\w9\1\s[10]\0\s[0]%(normtext)\_w[1200]I'm late! \_w[1200]I've got to get to work...!\n\n[half]\_w[2400]\1\s[10]%(fliptext)¡˙˙˙oN\n\n[half]\_w[2400]\s[12]˙˙˙oƃ ʇ,uop\n\n[half]\_w[2400]\0\s[0]%(normtext)But I have to be there. \_w[2400]If I don't show then I'll lose my job, \_w[1200]which means I cant pay for utilities, \_w[1200]which means- \_w[1200]Ah! \w9\w9\1\s[10]\0\s[0]%(normtext)\_w[1200]My head... \_w[3000]I can't even lift myself out of bed... \n\n[half]\_w[2400].\w9\w9.\w9\w9.\w9\w9I guess I have no choice but to call in sick for the week... \_w[2400]Maybe I just need more time to rest...\_w[2400]\1\s[13]%(fliptext)˙˙˙pooƃ ˙˙˙ʇsǝɹ"
}

